{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "本章描写了仵作萧百草在常笑的严刑逼供下，宁死不屈，最终自尽身亡的惨烈过程。萧百草临死前喊出的“鹦鹉”二字，引发了常笑对“血鹦鹉”案件的深度焦虑。随后，常笑通过审问安子豪，获知了关于血奴、老掌柜及其鹦鹉“小魔神”的线索，并决定立即前往鹦鹉楼进行调查。本章进一步加深了“血鹦鹉”背后的神秘氛围，并引出了关键人物血奴和王风。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_bai_cao",
      "text": "我不想你死，你就绝对死不了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_bai_cao",
      "speaker_name": "萧百草",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鹦鹉——",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鹦鹉？什么鹦鹉？血鹦鹉？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "这笼子里头本来有没有养鸟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "什么鸟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "鹦鹉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "偏就是这么巧，又是这种扁毛畜生。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "那只鹦鹉叫做小魔神，据讲是血奴送给老掌柜的礼物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "血奴为什么送他礼物？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "大概是因为他一生的积蓄都尽花在她的身上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "血奴今年有多大？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "好像不到二十。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "他今年又有多大？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "六十五怕也有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "这年纪，已足够做血奴的祖父了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "很足够的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "他这个年纪，是不是还有那个气力？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "不清楚，不过，听他说，那一夜，血奴连碰都不让他碰，可是他得到的刺激已令他满足。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "那一夜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "只一次就将一生的积蓄都花光？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "血奴的价钱很高。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "高得已足以花光他一生的积蓄？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "他却认为很值得，并说老天如果还让他再活十年，让他有机会再存那么多钱，一定会再到血奴那里一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "他的脑袋是不是有些问题？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "据我所知是没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "那么血奴莫非真有几下子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "听说是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "听说？你没有找过她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "我看你并不像很正经的那种男人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "本来就不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "你当然不会错过鹦鹉楼那种地方。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "到了鹦鹉楼，你竟然会不找血奴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我不能找她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "花不起那个价钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "勉强还花得起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "那为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "一定要回答？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "在我的面前只有死人才可以不必回答。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我跟她的母亲有来往，实在不好意思去找她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "原来是这个原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "方才你说过王风离开这里之后，就带着棺材到鹦鹉楼找血奴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "事实是这样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "鹦鹉楼在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "就在附近。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "林平、张铁留在这里，其他人随我到鹦鹉楼。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    }
  ],
